data.description: Charming 2 bed, 1 bath home with extensive renovations! Updates include new dimensional shingles and gutters (2019), vinyl siding (2021), vinyl flooring (2021) bathroom upgrades (2021), fresh interior paint (2021-22), and sleek black stainless steel kitchen appliances (2021), Wood deck out back (2021).  Basement features a B Dry System installed by Healthy Spaces.  With over 1600 sq ft, there's potential for additional bedrooms.  Don't miss out - schedule a viewing today before it's gone!!
